d Sadie\'s relationship to the test. Forget happily ever after - do theyeven have what it takes to make it to the altar?. ";s:8:"meta_key";s:23:"Comedy, License to Wed ";s:10:"searchkeys";s:22:"wedding,robin williams";s:6:"visits";s:3:"497";s:9:"published";s:1:"1";s:8:"ordering";s:1:"0";s:8:"featured";s:1:"0";s:14:"featured_order";s:1:"0";s:6:"access";s:6:"public";s:12:"published_up";s:19:"2008-04-17 01:01:46";s:14:"published_down";N;}i:2;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"id";s:2:"80";s:8:"category";s:2:"16";s:4:"item";s:13:"Blood Diamond";s:12:"item_creator";s:1:"0";s:11:"description";s:837:"Set against the backdrop of civil war and chaos in 1990\'s Sierra Leone, Blood Diamond is the story of Danny Archer - an ex mercenary from Zimbabwe - and Solomon Vandy - a Mende fisherman. Both men are African, but their histories as different as any can be, until their fates become joined in a common quest to recover a rare pink diamond that can transform their lives. While in prison for smuggling, Archer learns that Solomon - who was taken from his family and forced to work in the diamond fields - has found and hidden the extraordinary rough stone. With the help of Maddy Bowen, an American journalist whose idealism is tempered by a deepening connection with Archer, the two men embark on a trek through rebel territory, a journey that could save Solomon\'s family and give Archer the second chance he thought he would never have.";s:10:"date_added";s:1:"0";s:8:"modified";s:19:"2008-04-26 16:58:30";s:11:"modified_by";s:2:"62";s:5:"image";s:124:"a:2:{s:5:"image";s:36:"directcron/img_pictures/blooddia.jpg";s:9:"thumbnail";s:38:"directcron/img_thumbnails/blooddia.jpg";}";s:5:"video";N;s:8:"item_url";s:0:"";s:12:"templatefile";s:7:"oneitem";s:8:"metadesc";s:844:"Drama, Set against the backdrop of civil war and chaos in 1990\'s Sierra Leone, Blood Diamond is the story of Danny Archer - an ex mercenary from Zimbabwe - and Solomon Vandy - a Mende fisherman. Both men are African, but their historie